        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every box's items, at retail, are worth more than what you paid for that tier. That's the deal we make with you. If a box ever feels light, email us within 14 days and we'll refund the box, replace items, or credit your account.</p><p>No fine print. No hoops. We make our money on volume, not on you.</p>"
